<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">hi i have been playing this game for a while little over a year and a half and one thing that bugs the hell out of me is when i go to a website and look for gear that fits a certain class race and zone that it drops in sure this site has a filter for that to an extent but what i was thinking was to be able to select a zone like lets say sebilis then you click druid or whatever class and race item slot and it brings up a listing of items that drop in THAT zone only i think it would be so much of a help i have to go to eq beastiary and click on every goddamned monster too see what it drops then click on the item well anyway just a thought i was wondering if anyone else would like it too maybe we can get this site to start doing it i think it would be a great feature GNOME POWAH<br>
quintin 54 halfling druid<br>
